<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word" xml:lang="en"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v2"/><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v3"/><ttm:agent type="group" xml:id="v4"/><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v5"/><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v6"/><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v7"/><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v8"/><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v9"/><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v10"/><iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" leadingSilence="0"><translations><translation type="subtitle" xml:lang="zh-Hans"><text for="L21">没错 他潜入你梦境 乐见你尖叫 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(嘿)</span></text><text for="L20">他若唤你名字 万物隐进黑暗</text><text for="L23">我们不提布鲁诺</text><text for="L22">我们不提布鲁诺 不 不 不</text><text for="L25">他说我会发福 让他说中了 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(不 不)</span></text><text for="L24">他说我的鱼会死 第二天鱼真的死了 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(不 不)</span></text><text for="L27">预言既出 命中注定</text><text for="L26">他说我会头秃 结果你看看我的头 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(不 不)</span></text><text for="L29">将会成真 终有一天属于我</text><text for="L28">他说我梦想的生活</text><text for="L30">他说我的力量会增长</text><text for="L32">他说我的梦中情人</text><text for="L31">像藤上茁壮成长的葡萄 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(喂 马里亚诺在路上)</span></text><text for="L34">会与别人订婚</text><text for="L33">终将遥不可及</text><text for="L36">嘿 妹妹 我不想听到你出声</text><text for="L35">仿佛我现在就听到他说话</text><text for="L38">我现在就能听到他说话</text><text for="L37">仿佛我现在就能听到他说话</text><text for="L39">呃 布鲁诺</text><text for="L41">我真的需要了解布鲁诺</text><text for="L40">没错 说到那个布鲁诺</text><text for="L43">晚宴时间到</text><text for="L42">告诉我真相 全部真相 布鲁诺 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(伊莎贝拉 你的男朋友来了)</span></text><text for="L45">他若唤你名字 万物隐进黑暗 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(我们在做准备 天空万里无云)</span></text><text for="L44">身高七尺 背上爬老鼠 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(那天是我结婚的日子 那天是我们结婚的日子)</span></text><text for="L47">没错 他潜入你梦境 乐见你尖叫 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(布鲁诺坏笑着走了进来)</span></text><text for="L46">天空不许有一朵云</text><text for="L49">喂 马里亚诺在路上</text><text for="L48"><span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(雷声隆隆)</span> 你讲还是我讲</text><text for="L1">我们不提布鲁诺 不 不 不</text><text for="L2">我们不提布鲁诺 可是</text><text for="L50">布鲁诺说 看来要下雨 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(他说我的梦中情人终将遥不可及)</span></text><text for="L3">那天是我结婚的日子 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(那天是我们结婚的日子)</span></text><text for="L4">我们在做准备 天空万里无云 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(天空不许有一朵云)</span></text><text for="L52">那样做让我心绪难宁 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(会与别人 别人订婚)</span></text><text for="L5">布鲁诺坏笑着走了进来 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(雷声隆隆)</span></text><text for="L51">他为何说出来</text><text for="L6">你讲还是我讲 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(抱歉 亲爱的 请继续)</span></text><text for="L10">我们不提布鲁诺 不 不 不</text><text for="L54">他来了</text><text for="L7">布鲁诺说 看来要下雨 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(他为何说出来)</span></text><text for="L53">在狂风骤雨的天气结婚 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(我没事 我没事 我没事 我真的没事)</span></text><text for="L8">那样做让我心绪难宁 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(奶奶 请把雨伞拿出来)</span></text><text for="L12">嘿 从小就害怕布鲁诺开口讲话</text><text for="L56">我为何提起布鲁诺</text><text for="L9">在狂风骤雨的天气结婚 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(多么欢乐的一天 可不管怎样)</span></text><text for="L11">我们不提布鲁诺</text><text for="L55">不提布鲁诺</text><text for="L14">想起他 我就想到沙子滑落的声音 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(沙 沙 沙)</span></text><text for="L58">我真不该提起布鲁诺</text><text for="L13">我总是能听到他喃喃自语</text><text for="L57">绝口不提布鲁诺</text><text for="L16">总是让奶奶和家人手足无措</text><text for="L15">这份令人谦卑的天赋太沉重</text><text for="L18">你懂吗</text><text for="L17">让他们面对无法理解的预言</text><text for="L19">身高七尺 背上爬老鼠</text></translation></translations><songwriters><songwriter>Lin-Manuel Miranda</songwriter></songwriters><audio lyricOffset="0.046" role="spatial"/></iTunesMetadata></metadata></head><body dur="3:36.120"><div begin="1.152" end="10.254" itunes:songPart="Intro"><p begin="1.152" end="5.552" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1.152" end="1.528">We</span> <span begin="1.528" end="1.794">don't</span> <span begin="1.794" end="2.138">talk</span> <span begin="2.138" end="2.728">about</span> <span begin="2.728" end="3.236">Bru</span><span begin="3.236" end="3.738">no,</span> <span begin="3.845" end="4.394">no,</span> <span begin="4.394" end="4.998">no,</span> <span begin="4.998" end="5.552">no</span></p><p begin="5.838" end="10.254" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="5.838" end="6.214">We</span> <span begin="6.214" end="6.480">don't</span> <span begin="6.480" end="6.763">talk</span> <span begin="6.763" end="7.379">about</span> <span begin="7.379" end="7.874">Bru</span><span begin="7.874" end="9.149">no,</span> <span begin="9.686" end="10.254">but</span></p></div><div begin="10.522" end="43.125" itunes:songPart="Verse"><p begin="10.522" end="13.518" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="10.522" end="10.716">It</span> <span begin="10.716" end="10.908">was</span> <span begin="10.908" end="11.193">my</span> <span begin="11.193" end="11.759">wedding</span> <span begin="11.759" end="12.645">day</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="11.724" end="11.894">(It</span> <span begin="11.894" end="12.059">was</span> <span begin="12.059" end="12.314">our</span> <span begin="12.314" end="12.851">wedding</span> <span begin="12.851" end="13.518">day)</span></span></p><p begin="12.791" end="19.911" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="12.791" end="13.036">We</span> <span begin="13.036" end="13.236">were</span> <span begin="13.236" end="13.482">getting</span> <span begin="13.482" end="14.109">ready</span> <span begin="14.109" end="14.318">and</span> <span begin="14.318" end="14.627">there</span> <span begin="14.627" end="15.291">wasn't</span> <span begin="15.291" end="15.573">a</span> <span begin="15.573" end="16.132">cloud</span> <span begin="16.132" end="16.411">in</span> <span begin="16.411" end="16.718">the</span> <span begin="16.718" end="17.585">sky</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="16.943" end="17.272">(No</span> <span begin="17.272" end="17.629">clouds</span> <span begin="17.629" end="18.508">allowed</span> <span begin="18.508" end="18.803">in</span> <span begin="18.803" end="19.112">the</span> <span begin="19.112" end="19.911">sky)</span></span></p><p begin="19.257" end="24.640" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="19.257" end="19.886">Bruno</span> <span begin="19.886" end="20.179">walks</span> <span begin="20.179" end="20.806">in</span> <span begin="20.806" end="21.085">with</span> <span begin="21.085" end="21.337">a</span> <span begin="21.337" end="22.523">mischievous</span> <span begin="22.523" end="23.116">grin</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="23.119" end="23.714">(Thun</span><span begin="23.714" end="24.640">der)</span></span></p><p begin="24.262" end="29.397" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="24.262" end="24.496">You</span> <span begin="24.496" end="24.802">telling</span> <span begin="24.802" end="25.101">this</span> <span begin="25.101" end="25.599">story</span> <span begin="25.599" end="25.844">or</span> <span begin="25.844" end="26.018">am</span> <span begin="26.018" end="26.530">I?</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="26.615" end="26.903">(I'm</span> <span begin="26.903" end="27.181">sorry,</span> <span begin="27.181" end="27.315">mi</span> <span begin="27.315" end="27.674">vida,</span> <span begin="27.674" end="27.869">go</span> <span begin="27.869" end="29.397">on)</span></span></p><p begin="28.487" end="34.116" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="28.487" end="28.900">Bru</span><span begin="28.900" end="29.266">no</span> <span begin="29.266" end="29.596">says,</span> <span begin="29.596" end="29.849">"It</span> <span begin="29.849" end="30.315">looks</span> <span begin="30.315" end="30.688">like</span> <span begin="30.688" end="31.564">rain"</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="31.391" end="31.665">(Why</span> <span begin="31.665" end="31.797">did</span> <span begin="31.797" end="32.096">he</span> <span begin="32.096" end="32.439">tell</span> <span begin="32.439" end="34.116">us?)</span></span></p><p begin="32.977" end="38.719" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="32.977" end="33.350">In</span> <span begin="33.350" end="33.884">doing</span> <span begin="33.884" end="34.242">so,</span> <span begin="34.242" end="34.472">he</span> <span begin="34.472" end="34.950">floods</span> <span begin="34.950" end="35.390">my</span> <span begin="35.390" end="36.245">brain</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="35.712" end="36.212">(Abuela,</span> <span begin="36.212" end="36.340">get</span> <span begin="36.340" end="36.491">the</span> <span begin="36.491" end="36.773">um</span><span begin="36.773" end="37.067">brel</span><span begin="37.067" end="38.719">las)</span></span></p><p begin="37.894" end="43.125" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.894" end="38.585">Married</span> <span begin="38.585" end="38.834">in</span> <span begin="38.834" end="39.101">a</span> <span begin="39.101" end="40.020">hurri</span><span begin="40.020" end="40.888">cane</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="40.662" end="40.799">(What</span> <span begin="40.799" end="40.922">a</span> <span begin="40.922" end="41.482">joyous</span> <span begin="41.482" end="41.774">day,</span> <span begin="41.774" end="42.140">but</span> <span begin="42.140" end="42.609">any</span><span begin="42.609" end="43.125">way)</span></span></p></div><div begin="43.125" end="51.533" itunes:songPart="Bridge" ttm:agent="v4"><p begin="43.125" end="47.605" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v4"><span begin="43.125" end="43.524">We</span> <span begin="43.524" end="43.793">don't</span> <span begin="43.793" end="44.044">talk</span> <span begin="44.044" end="44.653">about</span> <span begin="44.653" end="45.253">Bru</span><span begin="45.253" end="45.640">no,</span> <span begin="45.791" end="46.434">no,</span> <span begin="46.434" end="47.018">no,</span> <span begin="47.018" end="47.605">no</span></p><p begin="47.798" end="51.533" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v4"><span begin="47.798" end="48.143">We</span> <span begin="48.143" end="48.450">don't</span> <span begin="48.450" end="48.704">talk</span> <span begin="48.704" end="49.316">about</span> <span begin="49.316" end="49.923">Bru</span><span begin="49.923" end="51.533">no</span></p></div><div begin="51.331" end="1:10.408" itunes:songPart="Verse" ttm:agent="v2"><p begin="51.331" end="54.202" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v2"><span beg